and set babel presets property useBuiltIns is 'usage'
then the polyfill will be loaded when Promise used
so this way has a bug when we webpack,if we use vuex without used Promise,always show the error: vuex requires a Promise polyfill in this browser.

so I have change the validate Promise way to:
```
      try {
        new Promise(() => {})
      } catch (error) {
        assert(false, `vuex requires a Promise polyfill in this browser.`)
      }
```

### Version
3.1.1

### Reproduction link
[https://new-issue.vuejs.org/?repo=vuejs/vuex](https://new-issue.vuejs.org/?repo=vuejs/vuex)







### Steps to reproduce
```
// 循环下去的主体是 module 没问题
  get(path) {
    return path.reduce((module, key) => {
      return module.getChild(key);
    }, this.root);
  }  

// 循环下去主体是 String，因此 module = module.getChild(key);
// module 永远指向 this.root
getNamespace(path) {
    let module = this.root;
    return path.reduce((namespace, key) => {
      module = module.getChild(key);
      return namespace   (module.namespaced ? key   '/' : '');
    }, '');
  }
```
`store._modules.getNamespace(['user','member'])` 将只能得到 `user/`

### What is expected?
`store._modules.getNamespace(['user','member'])` 应该得到 `user/member/` 的结果

### What is actually happening?
getNamespace(path) 返回的结果永远只有 root.getChild(key) 的匹配结果

